:"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [and it is said in one place in the TA that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miTorafN","text_ar":"مِطْرَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTorafN","text_ar":"مَطْرَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are dial. vars. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTorifN","text_ar":"مُطْرِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but I think that this last word is probably a mistake for ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTorafN","text_ar":"مُطْرَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taliydN","text_ar":"تَلِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taAlidN","text_ar":"تَالِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tilaAdN","text_ar":"تِلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl. of the first and third"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TurofN","text_ar":"طُرْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  Also, the first, A thing that is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and recent"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"new"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) what is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K, TA,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and coloured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of various colours,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing to the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of fruits and other things, (IAar, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mim~aA","text_ar":"مِمَّا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ystTrf bihi","text_ar":"يستطرف بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ystTrf","text_ar":"يستطرف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is evidently a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuTorafu","text_ar":"يُطْرَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such things as are given as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turaf","text_ar":"طُرَف"},{"kind":"text","text":"(pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Turofap","text_ar":"طُرْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":") meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rare and pleasing gifts"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA, from IAar.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TarifN","text_ar":"طَرِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter part, in three places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","IAar","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}